metrics.visualTitle: Répartion des DPE en fonction de l'état du logement

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Dim_batiment'[Etat], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			"Nb_DPE", 'Dim_DPE'[Nb_DPE]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE]", 'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE],
			"'Dim_batiment'[Etat]", 'Dim_batiment'[Etat],
			"Nb_DPE", [Nb_DPE]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE]", 'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [Nb_DPE]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE]),
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(201, __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns, [SortBy_DM0_0], 0, 'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE], 1)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Dim_batiment'[Etat])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Dim_batiment'[Etat], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Dim_batiment'[Etat],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Dim_batiment'[Etat]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'Dim_DPE'[Etiquette_DPE], [ColumnIndex]

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"AverageValeur", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('Dim_Conso'[Valeur]))
	)

metrics.visualTitle: Répartition des consommations des logements anciens

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Ancien"}, 'Dim_batiment'[Etat])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Dim_Conso'[Attribut],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"AverageValeur", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('Dim_Conso'[Valeur]))
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, [AverageValeur], 0, 'Dim_Conso'[Attribut], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[AverageValeur] DESC, 'Dim_Conso'[Attribut]

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"AverageAnnée_construction", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('Dim_batiment'[Année_construction]))
	)

metrics.visualTitle: Moyenne des consommations par année de construction

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Dim_batiment'[Année_construction],
			"AverageValeur", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('Dim_Conso'[Valeur]))
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'Dim_batiment'[Année_construction],
			[AverageValeur],
			350,
			,
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'Dim_batiment'[Année_construction]
